<pb ed="T" id="T21.1360.0878a" n="0878a"/>
<lb n="0878a01"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0878a02"/><head type="no">No. 1360 [cf. No. 1361]</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0878a03"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><title><note n="0878001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本，【甲】天平時代寫西福寺藏本，（佛說）＋六【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0878001"><lem>六</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">佛說六</rdg></app><note n="0878001" place="foot" type="rest">【原】麗本，【甲】天平時代寫西福寺藏本</note>門陀羅尼經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0878a04"/>
<lb n="0878a05"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0878002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔大〕－【明】，〔大唐…譯〕十一字－【甲】</note><note n="0878002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔大唐三藏法師玄奘奉詔譯〕十一字－【甲】，〔大〕－【明】</note><app n="0878002"><lem>大唐三藏法師玄奘奉　詔譯</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">唐三藏法師玄奘奉詔譯</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0878a06"/><p>如是我聞。一時薄伽梵。在淨居天上依空而
<lb n="0878a07"/>住眾妙七寶莊嚴道場。與無央數菩薩眾俱。
<lb n="0878a08"/>爾時世尊告諸菩薩。善男子若欲利益安樂
<lb n="0878a09"/>眾生。汝當受此六門陀羅尼法。謂我流轉於
<lb n="0878a10"/>生死中諸所受苦。勿令眾生同受斯苦。諸有
<lb n="0878a11"/>所受富貴世樂。願諸眾生同受斯樂。我所作
<lb n="0878a12"/>惡若未先悔終不發言稱無上法。我諸所有
<lb n="0878a13"/>眾魔之業若未先覺。終不舉心緣無上法。我
<lb n="0878a14"/>諸所有波羅蜜多所攝。一切世及出世廣大
<lb n="0878a15"/>善根。願諸眾生皆當速證無上智果。我證解
<lb n="0878a16"/>脫亦願眾生皆得解脫。勿令住著生死涅槃。
<lb n="0878a17"/>陀羅尼曰</p>
<lb n="0878a18"/><p type="dharani">懺謎懺謎<note place="inline">莫閉<note n="0878003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">反＝切【明】</note><app n="0878003"><lem>反</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">切</rdg></app></note>　羼諦羼諦　跋迭麗跋迭麗
<lb n="0878a19"/>　穌跋迭麗穌跋迭麗　諦誓諦誓戰迭麗戰迭
<lb n="0878a20"/>麗　戰迭邏伐底<note n="0878004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔丁履反〕－【三】</note><note n="0878004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔丁履反〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0878004"><lem><note place="inline">丁履<note n="0878005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">反＋（下同）【甲】</note><app n="0878005"><lem>反</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">反下同</rdg></app></note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>低殊伐底　達<note n="0878006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">磨＝摩【三】</note><note n="0878006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">磨＝摩【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0878006"><lem>磨</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">摩</rdg></app>伐
<lb n="0878a21"/>底　薩縛結&CB00619;鑠　毘輸達&CB00135;　薩縛阿<note n="0878007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">剌＝刺【甲】</note><app n="0878007"><lem>剌</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">刺</rdg></app>
<lb n="0878a22"/>託　<note n="0878008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">莎＝婆【三】</note><note n="0878008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">莎＝婆【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0878008"><lem>莎</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">婆</rdg></app>達&CB00135;　末諾僧輸達&CB00135;莎訶</p>
<lb n="0878a23"/><p>若有<note n="0878009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">清＝淨【三】【甲】</note><note n="0878009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">清＝淨【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0878009"><lem>清</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">淨</rdg></app>信善男子善女人。能於日夜六時。讀
<lb n="0878a24"/>誦如是六門陀羅尼者。此人<note n="0878010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔所有〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0878010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔所有〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0878010"><lem>所有</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>一切業障
<lb n="0878a25"/>皆悉消滅。疾悟阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。時薄
<lb n="0878a26"/>伽梵說是經已。一切菩薩摩訶薩及諸<note n="0878011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天＝大【三】</note><note n="0878011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">天＝大【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0878011"><lem>天</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">大</rdg></app>眾。
<lb n="0878a27"/>聞佛所說皆大歡喜信受奉行</p>
<lb n="0878a28"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead><note n="0878012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（佛說）＋六【三】</note><note n="0878012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（佛說）＋六【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0878012"><lem>六</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">佛說六</rdg></app>門陀羅尼經</jhead></juan></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>
